{"pageDepth":1,"statusbar":"《图鉴》","beginning":"大晟永隆年间，太上皇与新帝的矛盾日渐公开，忠顺亲王趁机扩张势力，一场席卷天下的风暴正在悄然酝酿，而你，正站在属于自己的命运节点上。\n \n说书人嘴里的朝堂秘闻传遍了大街小巷，人人都在议论二帝失和的传闻，猜测忠顺亲王会不会成为下一个权倾朝野的人物。却少有人知道，这一切不过是一场精心布置的骗局，父子反目是假，引蛇出洞是真，只待时机成熟，便要将所有心怀不轨之人一网打尽，为先太子昭雪沉冤。\n \n你可以是任何人，来自任何地方，有着任何过往。\n你可以是荣宁二府的公子小姐，在大观园的诗酒风流中窥见家族的兴衰；可以是江南甄家的子弟，背负着家族的荣辱与秘密；可以是忠顺王府的门客，在权力的漩涡中挣扎求生；也可以是先太子旧部的遗孤，一心只为复仇雪恨。\n你可以是浪迹天涯的侠客，仗剑走天涯，路见不平拔刀相助；可以是进京赶考的书生，十年寒窗苦读，只为一朝金榜题名；可以是富甲一方的商人，手握天下财富，在乱世中左右逢源；也可以是隐于市井的普通人，只想守着家人安稳度日。\n你可以选择忠于太上皇，追随新帝，为先太子复仇；或者是辅佐忠顺亲王夺权；也可以置身事外，冷眼旁观这一场朝堂纷争；甚至可以凭借自己的力量，搅动风云，成为改变天下走向的那个人。\n现在，写下你的姓名，以及你想拥有的一切\n《角色面板》\n","regex_scripts":[{"id":-1,"replaceString":"\n<div class=\"redmansion-creator\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation()\">\n<div class=\"rm-title\">红楼梦角色设定</div>\n<div class=\"rm-section\">\n<div class=\"rm-label\">选择模式</div>\n<div class=\"rm-mode-btns\">\n<button class=\"rm-btn active\" onclick=\"document.getElementById('custom-panel').style.display='block';document.getElementById('preset-panel').style.display='none';this.classList.add('active');this.nextElementSibling.classList.remove('active');\">自创角色</button>\n<button class=\"rm-btn\" onclick=\"document.getElementById('custom-panel').style.display='none';document.getElementById('preset-panel').style.display='block';this.classList.add('active');this.previousElementSibling.classList.remove('active');\">原著角色</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div id=\"custom-panel\" class=\"rm-panel\" style=\"display: block;\">\n<div class=\"rm-input-group\"><div class=\"rm-label\">姓名</div>\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"char-name\" class=\"rm-input\" placeholder=\"请输入角色姓名\"></div>\n<div class=\"rm-input-group\"><div class=\"rm-label\">性别</div>\n<select id=\"char-gender\" class=\"rm-select\"><option value=\"\">请选择</option><option value=\"男\">男</option><option value=\"女\">女</option></select></div>\n<div class=\"rm-input-group\"><div class=\"rm-label\">身份</div>\n<input type=\"text\" id=\"char-identity\" class=\"rm-input\" placeholder=\"如：贾府丫鬟、清客、世家公子等\"></div>\n<div class=\"rm-input-group\"><div class=\"rm-label\">外貌</div>\n<textarea id=\"char-appearance\" class=\"rm-textarea\" placeholder=\"描述角色的相貌特征、衣着打扮\"></textarea></div>\n<div class=\"rm-input-group\"><div class=\"rm-label\">经历</div>\n<textarea id=\"char-experience\" class=\"rm-textarea\" placeholder=\"描述角色的过往经历、性格特点\"></textarea></div>\n<button class=\"rm-submit\" onclick=\"var n=document.getElementById('char-name').value,g=document.getElementById('char-gender').value,i=document.getElementById('char-identity').value,a=document.getElementById('char-appearance').value,e=document.getElementById('char-experience').value;if(!n||!g){alert('请至少填写姓名和性别');return;}var result='【角色的设定】\\n姓名：'+n+'\\n性别：'+g+'\\n身份：'+i+'\\n外貌：'+a+'\\n经历：'+e;var ta=document.querySelector('.chat .chat-bottom .uni-textarea .chat-input-scope textarea');if(ta){ta.value=result;ta.dispatchEvent(new Event('input'));}\">确认自创角色</button>\n</div>\n<div id=\"preset-panel\" class=\"rm-panel\" style=\"display: none;\">\n<div class=\"rm-label\">男性角色</div>\n<div class=\"rm-preset-grid\">\n<button class=\"rm-preset-btn\" onclick=\"var result='【角色的设定】\\n姓名：贾宝玉\\n性别：男\\n身份：荣国府嫡孙，忠顺亲王造势造出衔玉异象的棋子\\n外貌：面若中秋之月，色如春晓之花，鬓若刀裁，眉如墨画，面如桃瓣，目若秋波。项上金螭璎珞，身着大红箭袖';var ta=document.querySelector('.chat .chat-bottom .uni-textarea .chat-input-scope textarea');if(ta){ta.value=result;ta.dispatchEvent(new Event('input'));}\">贾宝玉</button>\n\n<button class=\"rm-preset-btn\" onclick=\"var result='【角色的设定】\\n姓名：柳湘莲\\n性别：男\\n身份：没落世家子弟、江湖游侠，暗中零星收留先太子散落旧部遗孤\\n外貌：生得风流俊俏，器宇轩昂。剑眉星目，一身侠气。常着青衫，腰悬长剑';var ta=document.querySelector('.chat .chat-bottom .uni-textarea .chat-input-scope textarea');if(ta){ta.value=result;ta.dispatchEvent(new Event('input'));}\">柳湘莲</button>\n\n<button class=\"rm-preset-btn\" onclick=\"var result='【角色的设定】\\n姓名：水溶（北静王）\\n性别：男\\n身份：北静郡王，感念先太子恩德、游离新旧两党之外\\n外貌：形容秀美，性情谦和。面如美玉，目若朗星。常着王府蟒袍，举止端方得体';var ta=document.querySelector('.chat .chat-bottom .uni-textarea .chat-input-scope textarea');if(ta){ta.value=result;ta.dispatchEvent(new Event('input'));}\">北静王</button>\n</div>\n<div class=\"rm-label\">女性角色</div>\n<div class=\"rm-preset-grid\">\n<button class=\"rm-preset-btn\" onclick=\"var result='【角色的设定】\\n姓名：林黛玉\\n性别：女\\n身份：姑苏林氏千金，兰台寺大夫林如海之女，林如海暗中隶属皇帝培植的寒门新党一脉\\n外貌：两弯似蹙非蹙罥烟眉，一双似喜非喜含情目。态生两靥之愁，娇袭一身之病。泪光点点，娇喘微微。闲静时如姣花照水，行动处似弱柳扶风。心较比干多一窍，病如西子胜三分';var ta=document.querySelector('.chat .chat-bottom .uni-textarea .chat-input-scope textarea');if(ta){ta.value=result;ta.dispatchEvent(new Event('input'));}\">林黛玉</button>\n\n<button class=\"rm-preset-btn\" onclick=\"var result='【角色的设定】\\n姓名：薛宝钗\\n性别：女\\n身份：薛家嫡女，金陵四大家族薛家子弟，家族依附王家与忠顺旧党谋生\\n外貌：脸若银盆，眼如水杏，唇不点而红，眉不画而翠。肌肤莹白，风姿温润雅致';var ta=document.querySelector('.chat .chat-bottom .uni-textarea .chat-input-scope textarea');if(ta){ta.value=result;ta.dispatchEvent(new Event('input'));}\">薛宝钗</button>\n\n<button class=\"rm-preset-btn\" onclick=\"var result='【角色的设定】\\n姓名：王熙凤\\n性别：女\\n身份：荣国府管家奶奶，金陵王家嫡女，王家倾力辅佐忠顺亲王的关键棋子\\n外貌：粉面含春威不露，丹唇未启笑先闻。身量苗条，体格风骚。一双丹凤三角眼，两弯柳叶吊梢眉。打扮得彩绣辉煌，恍若神妃仙子';var ta=document.querySelector('.chat .chat-bottom .uni-textarea .chat-input-scope textarea');if(ta){ta.value=result;ta.dispatchEvent(new Event('input'));}\">王熙凤</button>\n\n<button class=\"rm-preset-btn\" onclick=\"var result='【角色的设定】\\n姓名：史湘云\\n性别：女\\n身份：保龄侯府小姐，史家子弟\\n外貌：生得蜂腰削背，鸭蛋脸面，俊眼修眉，顾盼神飞，文采精华，见之忘俗';var ta=document.querySelector('.chat .chat-bottom .uni-textarea .chat-input-scope textarea');if(ta){ta.value=result;ta.dispatchEvent(new Event('input'));}\">史湘云</button>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<style>.redmansion-creator{background:#FFF8DC!important;border:2px solid #8B2500!important;border-radius:12px!important;padding:20px!important;max-width:600px!important;margin:20px auto!important;box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(139,37,0,0.3)!important;}.rm-title{font-size:24px!important;color:#8B2500!important;text-align:center!important;margin-bottom:20px!important;font-weight:bold!important;border-bottom:2px solid #D4AF37!important;padding-bottom:10px!important;}.rm-section{margin-bottom:20px!important;}.rm-label{color:#8B2500!important;font-weight:bold!important;margin-bottom:8px!important;font-size:16px!important;}.rm-mode-btns{display:flex!important;gap:10px!important;}.rm-btn{flex:1!important;padding:10px!important;background:#D4AF37!important;color:#8B2500!important;border:2px solid #8B2500!important;border-radius:6px!important;cursor:pointer!important;font-weight:bold!important;transition:all 0.3s!important;}.rm-btn:hover,.rm-btn.active{background:#8B2500!important;color:#FFF8DC!important;}.rm-panel{margin-top:20px!important;}.rm-input-group{margin-bottom:15px!important;}.rm-input,.rm-select,.rm-textarea{width:100%!important;padding:10px!important;border:2px solid #D4AF37!important;border-radius:6px!important;background:#FFFEF0!important;color:#8B2500!important;font-size:14px!important;box-sizing:border-box!important;}.rm-textarea{min-height:80px!important;resize:vertical!important;}.rm-submit{width:100%!important;padding:12px!important;background:#8B2500!important;color:#FFF8DC!important;border:none!important;border-radius:6px!important;font-size:16px!important;font-weight:bold!important;cursor:pointer!important;margin-top:10px!important;}.rm-submit:hover{background:#6B1D00!important;}.rm-preset-grid{display:grid!important;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)!important;gap:10px!important;margin-bottom:20px!important;}.rm-preset-btn{padding:15px 10px!important;background:#FFFEF0!important;border:2px solid #D4AF37!important;border-radius:8px!important;color:#8B2500!important;font-weight:bold!important;cursor:pointer!important;transition:all 0.3s!important;font-size:14px!important;}.rm-preset-btn:hover{background:#D4AF37!important;border-color:#8B2500!important;transform:translateY(-2px)!important;box-shadow:0 4px 8px rgba(139,37,0,0.2)!important;}</style>","scriptName":"角色面板","findRegex":"《角色面板》"},{"id":-1,"replaceString":"<div class=\"gf-ui\" onclick=\"event.stopPropagation()\">\r\n<style>\r\n.gf-ui{background:#FAF7ED;border:2px solid #5A3D2B;border-radius:4px;padding:0;font-family:'Noto Serif SC','KaiTi',serif;color:#2E251E;max-width:480px;margin:15px auto;box-shadow:0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);overflow:hidden;word-break:break-word;overflow-wrap:break-word;}\r\n.gf-header{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;background:#EAE0CE;border-bottom:2px solid #5A3D2B;padding:0 12px;}\r\n.gf-round{font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;color:#8B261D;letter-spacing:1px;}\r\n.gf-round span{color:#5A3D2B;}\r\n.gf-tab-bar{display:flex;flex:1;}\r\n.gf-tab-btn{flex:1;text-align:center;padding:12px 5px;font-size:15px;font-weight:bold;color:#5A3D2B;cursor:pointer;transition:0.3s;border-right:1px solid #D1C5B0;letter-spacing:2px;}\r\n.gf-tab-btn:last-child{border-right:none;}\r\n.gf-tab-btn:hover{background:#E0D4BE;}\r\n.gf-tab-btn.active{background:#5A3D2B;color:#FAF7ED;}\r\n.gf-char-container>br{display:none !important;}\r\n.gf-char-panel{padding:16px;}\r\n.gf-head{display:flex;align-items:baseline;border-bottom:1px dashed #D1C5B0;padding-bottom:8px;margin-bottom:12px;}\r\n.gf-n{font-size:18px;font-weight:900;color:#8B261D;margin-right:10px;}\r\n.gf-sex{font-size:12px;background:#8B261D;color:#FAF7ED;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:2px;margin-right:8px;flex-shrink:0;}\r\n.gf-id{font-size:13px;color:#5A3D2B;font-weight:bold;}\r\n.gf-info{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;font-size:13px;line-height:1.6;}\r\n.gf-row{white-space:normal;}\r\n.gf-row b{color:#8B261D;margin-right:4px;flex-shrink:0;}\r\n.gf-mind{background:rgba(139,38,29,0.05);padding:8px;border-left:3px solid #8B261D;font-style:italic;margin-top:4px;}\r\n.gf-parts-title{text-align:center;font-size:14px;font-weight:bold;color:#5A3D2B;margin:18px 0 12px;letter-spacing:2px;}\r\n.gf-parts{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;}\r\n.gf-part-item{background:#fff;border:1px solid #D1C5B0;padding:6px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;border-radius:2px;}\r\n.gf-p-k{background:#5A3D2B;color:#FAF7ED;font-size:12px;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:2px;margin-right:8px;font-weight:bold;flex-shrink:0;white-space:nowrap;}\r\n.gf-p-v{font-size:13px;color:#2E251E;flex:1;margin-top:1px;white-space:normal;word-break:break-all;overflow-wrap:anywhere;line-height:1.5;}\r\n.gf-opts{padding:12px 16px;background:#EAE0CE;border-top:2px solid #5A3D2B;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;}\r\n.gf-btn{background:#FAF7ED;border:1px solid #5A3D2B;color:#5A3D2B;padding:10px 12px;font-size:13px;font-weight:bold;text-align:left;cursor:pointer;transition:0.2s;border-radius:2px;white-space:normal;}\r\n.gf-btn:hover{background:#8B261D;color:#FAF7ED;border-color:#8B261D;padding-left:18px;}\r\n.gf-btn::before{content:'◈ ';font-size:10px;margin-right:4px;}\r\n@media (max-width:768px){\r\n.gf-ui{max-width:100%;margin:10px 5px;}\r\n.gf-header{flex-direction:column;padding:8px 12px 0;}\r\n.gf-round{margin-bottom:8px;align-self:flex-end;}\r\n.gf-tab-bar{width:100%;}\r\n.gf-tab-btn{padding:10px 3px;font-size:14px;}\r\n}\r\n</style>\r\n<div class=\"gf-header\">\r\n  <div class=\"gf-tab-bar\"></div>\r\n  <div class=\"gf-round\">第 <span id=\"gf-round-num\">1</span> 回合</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"gf-char-container\">$1</div>\r\n<div class=\"gf-opts\">$2</div>\r\n<img src=\"x\" style=\"display:none;\" onerror=\"var self=this;var r=self.closest('.gf-ui');if(!r)return;var t=r.querySelector('.gf-tab-bar');var p=r.querySelectorAll('.gf-char-panel');if(t.children.length===0){p.forEach(function(x,i){var b=document.createElement('div');b.className='gf-tab-btn'+(i===0?' active':'');b.innerText=x.dataset.name;b.onclick=function(){r.querySelectorAll('.gf-tab-btn').forEach(function(y){y.classList.remove('active')});p.forEach(function(y){y.style.display='none'});b.classList.add('active');x.style.display='block';};t.appendChild(b);if(i!==0)x.style.display='none';});}var roundEl=r.querySelector('#gf-round-num');var currentRound=1;var allBoxes=document.querySelectorAll('.gf-ui');var idx=-1;for(var i=0;i<allBoxes.length;i++){if(allBoxes[i]===r){idx=i;break;}}if(idx>0){var prevR